with open arms,

302
00:17:50,212 --> 00:17:52,279
and now I gotta get down
on my hands and knees

303
00:17:52,281 --> 00:17:53,780
and beg 'em to stay?

304
00:17:53,782 --> 00:17:55,115
There's a fight coming.

305
00:17:55,117 --> 00:17:57,418
