337
00:19:24,370 --> 00:19:25,869
<i>Come on.</i>

338
00:19:28,041 --> 00:19:30,241
God damn it.

339
00:20:14,649 --> 00:20:17,483
<i>Looking for something
to take out the old man?</i>

340
