00:22:16,533 --> 00:22:18,533
I want you all at attention.

374
00:22:26,243 --> 00:22:29,611
All right.
That's a start.

375
00:22:29,613 --> 00:22:31,112
Tracking Mike down and beating
his ass into the ground,

376
00:22:31,114 --> 00:22:32,514
that'd be a start.

