his name again.

380
00:22:41,224 --> 00:22:45,226
From now on, we set an example.

381
00:22:45,228 --> 00:22:47,695
We become a model
of what this place needs--

382
00:22:47,697 --> 00:22:51,432
order, discipline,

383
00:22:51,434 --> 00:22:54,102
