00:25:13,339 --> 00:25:15,272
So why don't
you just crash here?

422
00:25:21,412 --> 00:25:24,014
This is a scared spot, you know.

423
00:25:24,016 --> 00:25:27,583
<i>Me and Vern and Russell
and McCarthy,</i>

424
00:25:27,585 --> 00:25:29,886
we sat here one night and...

